title: (x) Can you help ID this Font? / Slab w/ single-sidedly bracketed serifs - Stag {Jan}
content: Can anyone identify this font? Both the Headline (capped) copy and the subhead. I would greatly appreciate it.
author: dongura

comments.content: It's from the Invisible Family, aka Sans-Font.
